<p id="fs-id1170572137475">Express <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mn>210</mn><mtext>&#176;</mtext></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mn>210</mn><mtext>&#176;</mtext></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> using radians. Express <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mn>11</mn><mi>&#960;</mi><mtext>/</mtext><mn>6</mn></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mn>11</mn><mi>&#960;</mi><mtext>/</mtext><mn>6</mn></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> rad using degrees.</p>
